    "They formulated a joint resource allocation and trajectory optimization problem.",
    "Moreover, they considered the optimization problem as an MDP and developed two DRL-based algorithms to deal with it, respectively.",
    "Wang et al. [246] proposed a CNN-based rapid deployment strategy for UAV-ISAC systems, where the UAV acted as an airborne ISAC-BS to offer dual services to the disaster area.",
    "They first established a labeled data set consisting of pairs of user locations and UAV positions, and then trained a CNN in an SL manner to learn the mapping from the user distributions to the optimal UAV deployment position.",
